This Enhanced Calculator is designed to handle all your basic arithmetic needs with ease and precision. It supports addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division with a user-friendly interface. The calculator allows you to perform lengthy calculations by continuously appending numbers and operators, giving you flexibility similar to a physical calculator.

Key Uses:

Quick calculations for daily math problems

Long, multi-step arithmetic operations without losing track

Easy error correction with backspace and clear functions

Works seamlessly on both desktop and mobile devices

Light and dark mode for comfortable use in any lighting

Why Use This Calculator:
It combines a modern design with smooth animations for a pleasant experience, while also providing practical features like theme toggling and error handling. Perfect for students, professionals, or anyone needing a reliable tool for on-the-go math.
